snippet.textDisplay:
Such a famous Qawwali and the saddest part is no one know who the poet is. 
Well, this is written by a Qawwal from Lucknow, UP, India. He even filed a case against Sabri Brothers for not giving him the credit of his work. But because of the partition and some financial reasons, he lost the case. 
People have got the fame by this qawwali and the poet died along with his dream to go to Medina.
